[Metal self-expanding stents for malignant obstruction of stomach outlet and 
duodenum].

[Article in Russian; Abstract available in Russian from the publisher]

Shabunin AV(1), Lebedev SS(1), Chechenin GM(1), Barinov YV(1), Sidorova YV(1), 
