Knee osteoarthritis has doubled in prevalence since the mid-20th century.

Wallace IJ(1), Worthington S(2), Felson DT(3), Jurmain RD(4), Wren KT(5), 
Maijanen H(6), Woods RJ(7), Lieberman DE(8).

